ualTo(TestClassAwareParameterTheory.class);\n            assertThat(signature.getType()).isEqualTo(String.class);\n            return Collections.singletonList(PotentialAssignment.forValue(\"word\", \"test-class-aware\"));\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}
